00:42:20.380 --> 00:42:21.509
Comandante de la Vanguardia.

00:42:22.080 --> 00:42:24.449
Destruyan Heunghwajin hoy mismo.

00:42:24.449 --> 00:42:25.480
Fracasen,

00:42:26.949 --> 00:42:30.659
